      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, with recent attention paid to the rear subframe reinforcement and trailing arm bushings. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering a perfect balance of compliance and lateral grip. While the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain is in excellent health, delivering a linear power band and that signature metallic exhaust note. A true driver\u2019s spec with all major mechanical hurdles addressed.",
